START| EXCURSIONS, FOOD, RELAX| Welcome to the beautiful beaches of Jamaica! You've just arrived and can't wait to start your adventure. Do you want to a) explore exciting excursions, b) try delicious Jamaican food, c) or simply relax on the beach?

EXCURSIONS| WATER_SPORTS, ISLAND_TOUR, DOLPHIN_ENCOUNTER| You've chosen to explore exciting excursions. Do you want to a) try water sports, b) go on an island tour, or c) experience a dolphin encounter?

WATER_SPORTS| JET_SKI, PARASAILING| Ready for some adrenaline? Choose a) to ride a jet ski or b) try parasailing.

JET_SKI|| You zoom across the crystal-clear waters, feeling the wind in your hair. What a thrilling ride!

PARASAILING|| Soar high above the beach, enjoying breathtaking views of the coastline. What an exhilarating experience!

ISLAND_TOUR| WATERFALL_HIKE, HISTORICAL_SITES| You've opted for an island tour. Will you a) hike to a stunning waterfall or b) explore historical sites?

WATERFALL_HIKE|| Trek through lush greenery to discover a hidden waterfall. The natural beauty is awe-inspiring!

HISTORICAL_SITES|| Immerse yourself in Jamaica's rich history, exploring ancient sites and learning fascinating stories.

DOLPHIN_ENCOUNTER|| You interact with playful dolphins, creating memories that will last a lifetime. What an incredible experience!

FOOD| JAMAICAN_JERK, SEAFOOD_FEAST| Time to savor the local cuisine. Do you crave a) Jamaican jerk dishes or b) a feast of fresh seafood?

JAMAICAN_JERK|| Indulge in the bold and spicy flavors of Jamaican jerk chicken and pork. Your taste buds are dancing with joy!

SEAFOOD_FEAST|| Feast on a variety of freshly caught seafood. The flavors of the ocean are a delightful symphony on your palate.

RELAX| SUNBATHING, BEACH_BAR| Opting for relaxation. Do you want to a) sunbathe on the pristine sands or b) visit a lively beach bar?

SUNBATHING|| Bask in the warm Jamaican sun, listening to the soothing sound of waves. Pure bliss!

BEACH_BAR|| Dance to the rhythmic beats, sip on tropical cocktails, and make new friends at the vibrant beach bar.

